{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0115q1FPXBqNPVQgv1iaSwAc","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.panache;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\n     4→import java.util.Optional;\n     5→import java.util.UUID;\n     6→import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;\n     7→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.FollowRelationship;\n     8→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.FollowRelationshipRepository;\n     9→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.User;\n    10→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.EntityUtils;\n    11→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.FollowRelationshipEntity;\n    12→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.FollowRelationshipEntityKey;\n    13→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.UserEntity;\n    14→\n    15→@ApplicationScoped\n    16→@AllArgsConstructor\n    17→public class FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache\n    18→    extends AbstractPanacheRepository<FollowRelationshipEntity, FollowRelationshipEntityKey>\n    19→    implements FollowRelationshipRepository {\n    20→\n    21→  private final EntityUtils entityUtils;\n    22→\n    23→  @Override\n    24→  public boolean isFollowing(UUID currentUserId, UUID followedUserId) {\n    25→    Long count = em.createQuery(\n    26→            \"SELECT COUNT(e) FROM FollowRelationshipEntity e WHERE e.primaryKey.user.id = :currentUserId and e.primaryKey.followed.id = :followedUserId\",\n    27→            Long.class)\n    28→        .setParameter(\"currentUserId\", currentUserId)\n    29→        .setParameter(\"followedUserId\", followedUserId)\n    30→        .getSingleResult();\n    31→    return count > 0;\n    32→  }\n    33→\n    34→  @Override\n    35→  public void save(FollowRelationship followRelationship) {\n    36→    final var userEntity = findUserEntityById(followRelationship.getUser().getId());\n    37→    final var userToFollowEntity = findUserEntityById(followRelationship.getFollowed().getId());\n    38→    FollowRelationshipEntity entity = new FollowRelationshipEntity(userEntity, userToFollowEntity);\n    39→    em.persist(entity);\n    40→    em.flush();\n    41→  }\n    42→\n    43→  @Override\n    44→  public Optional<FollowRelationship> findByUsers(User loggedUser, User followedUser) {\n    45→    return findUsersFollowedEntityByUsers(loggedUser, followedUser)\n    46→        .map(this::followingRelationship);\n    47→  }\n    48→\n    49→  @Override\n    50→  public void remove(FollowRelationship followRelationship) {\n    51→    final var usersFollowedEntity =\n    52→        findUsersFollowedEntityByUsers(\n    53→                followRelationship.getUser(), followRelationship.getFollowed())\n    54→            .orElseThrow();\n    55→    em.remove(em.merge(usersFollowedEntity));\n    56→  }\n    57→\n    58→  private Optional<FollowRelationshipEntity> findUsersFollowedEntityByUsers(\n    59→      User loggedUser, User followedUser) {\n    60→    final var loggedUserEntity = findUserEntityById(loggedUser.getId());\n    61→    final var followedEntity = findUserEntityById(followedUser.getId());\n    62→    final var key = usersFollowedKey(loggedUserEntity, followedEntity);\n    63→    return Optional.ofNullable(em.find(FollowRelationshipEntity.class, key));\n    64→  }\n    65→\n    66→  private FollowRelationship followingRelationship(\n    67→      FollowRelationshipEntity followRelationshipEntity) {\n    68→    final var user = entityUtils.user(followRelationshipEntity.getUser());\n    69→    final var followed = entityUtils.user(followRelationshipEntity.getFollowed());\n    70→    return new FollowRelationship(user, followed);\n    71→  }\n    72→\n    73→  private FollowRelationshipEntityKey usersFollowedKey(UserEntity user, UserEntity followed) {\n    74→    final var primaryKey = new FollowRelationshipEntityKey();\n    75→    primaryKey.setUser(user);\n    76→    primaryKey.setFollowed(followed);\n    77→    return primaryKey;\n    78→  }\n    79→}\n    80→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LCBNthBJ7SZpqr62bdGvHP","session_id":"9cccbbd3-df4b-4bdc-8bbb-45d794239170","uuid":"18f03722-ef7a-4b6c-b321-13dc872d44e5"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_0191Et5unBoFzDsMnemPjdbP","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.panache;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\n     4→import java.util.List;\n     5→import java.util.stream.Collectors;\n     6→import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;\n     7→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.Article;\n     8→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.TagRelationship;\n     9→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.TagRelationshipRepository;\n    10→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.tag.Tag;\n    11→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.EntityUtils;\n    12→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.TagRelationshipEntity;\n    13→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.TagRelationshipEntityKey;\n    14→\n    15→@ApplicationScoped\n    16→@AllArgsConstructor\n    17→public class TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache\n    18→    extends AbstractPanacheRepository<TagRelationshipEntity, TagRelationshipEntityKey>\n    19→    implements TagRelationshipRepository {\n    20→\n    21→  private final EntityUtils entityUtils;\n    22→\n    23→  @Override\n    24→  public void save(TagRelationship tagRelationship) {\n    25→    final var articleEntity = findArticleEntityById(tagRelationship.getArticle().getId());\n    26→    final var tagEntity = findTagEntityById(tagRelationship.getTag().getId());\n    27→    em.persist(new TagRelationshipEntity(articleEntity, tagEntity));\n    28→  }\n    29→\n    30→  @Override\n    31→  public List<Tag> findArticleTags(Article article) {\n    32→    return em.createQuery(\n    33→            \"from TagRelationshipEntity as tagRelationship where tagRelationship.primaryKey.article.id = :articleId\",\n    34→            TagRelationshipEntity.class)\n    35→        .setParameter(\"articleId\", article.getId())\n    36→        .getResultList()\n    37→        .stream()\n    38→        .map(entityUtils::tag)\n    39→        .collect(Collectors.toList());\n    40→  }\n    41→}\n    42→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LCBNthBJ7SZpqr62bdGvHP","session_id":"9cccbbd3-df4b-4bdc-8bbb-45d794239170","uuid":"d0159b76-15f2-4fa7-927d-e921a0943875"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_011xWMacP6Uj85TRtxseBgW1","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRepositoryPanache.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.panache;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\n     4→import java.util.List;\n     5→import java.util.Optional;\n     6→import java.util.UUID;\n     7→import java.util.stream.Collectors;\n     8→import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;\n     9→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.tag.Tag;\n    10→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.tag.TagRepository;\n    11→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.EntityUtils;\n    12→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.hibernate.entity.TagEntity;\n    13→\n    14→@ApplicationScoped\n    15→@AllArgsConstructor\n    16→public class TagRepositoryPanache extends AbstractPanacheRepository<TagEntity, UUID>\n    17→    implements TagRepository {\n    18→\n    19→  private final EntityUtils entityUtils;\n    20→\n    21→  @Override\n    22→  public List<Tag> findAllTags() {\n    23→    return em.createQuery(\"FROM TagEntity\", TagEntity.class)\n    24→        .getResultList()\n    25→        .stream()\n    26→        .map(entityUtils::tag)\n    27→        .collect(Collectors.toList());\n    28→  }\n    29→\n    30→  @Override\n    31→  public Optional<Tag> findByName(String name) {\n    32→    return em.createQuery(\"FROM TagEntity WHERE upper(name) = ?1\", TagEntity.class)\n    33→        .setParameter(1, name.toUpperCase().trim())\n    34→        .getResultStream()\n    35→        .findFirst()\n    36→        .map(entityUtils::tag);\n    37→  }\n    38→\n    39→  @Override\n    40→  public void save(Tag tag) {\n    41→    em.persist(new TagEntity(tag));\n    42→  }\n    43→\n    44→  @Override\n    45→  public List<Tag> findByNames(List<String> names) {\n    46→    final var tagsEntity = em.createQuery(\n    47→            \"select tags from TagEntity as tags where upper(tags.name) in (:names)\",\n    48→            TagEntity.class)\n    49→        .setParameter(\"names\", toUpperCase(names))\n    50→        .getResultList();\n    51→    return tagsEntity.stream().map(entityUtils::tag).collect(Collectors.toList());\n    52→  }\n    53→}\n    54→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LCBNthBJ7SZpqr62bdGvHP","session_id":"9cccbbd3-df4b-4bdc-8bbb-45d794239170","uuid":"27d32128-0347-4999-b2e4-2e6144831c54"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LCBNthBJ7SZpqr62bdGvHP","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully rewritten all 7 Panache repository files to use standard JPA EntityManager instead of Quarkus Panache APIs. Here's a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Files Rewritten\n\n### 1. **UserRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/UserRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Key changes:**\n- Removed static import of `io.quarkus.panache.common.Parameters.with`\n- `persist(entity)` → `em.persist(entity)`\n- `count(\"upper(field)\", value)` → `em.createQuery(\"SELECT COUNT(e) FROM UserEntity e WHERE upper(e.field) = ?1\", Long.class)`\n- `find(\"upper(email)\", value).firstResultOptional()` → `em.createQuery().getResultStream().findFirst()`\n- `findByIdOptional(id)` → `Optional.ofNullable(em.find(UserEntity.class, id))`\n- `findById(id)` → `em.find(UserEntity.class, id)`\n\n### 2. **ArticleRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/ArticleRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Key changes:**\n- Removed imports of `io.quarkus.panache.common.Page`, `Parameters`, and `Sort`\n- `persistAndFlush(entity)` → `em.persist(entity); em.flush()`\n- `deleteById(id)` → `em.find()` then `em.remove()`\n- `find().page(Page.of(offset, limit))` → `setFirstResult(offset).setMaxResults(limit)`\n- `Sort.descending(\"field\")` → Added `ORDER BY field DESC` in JPQL queries\n- `Parameters.with(\"key\", val)` → Direct parameter setting with `query.setParameter(\"key\", val)`\n\n### 3. **CommentRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/CommentRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Key changes:**\n- Removed static imports and `Parameters` import\n- `find(\"query\", params).firstResultOptional()` → `em.createQuery().getResultStream().findFirst()`\n- `delete(entity)` → `em.remove(em.merge(entity))`\n- `find(\"query\", params).list()` → `em.createQuery().getResultList()`\n\n### 4. **FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Key changes:**\n- Removed static import of `Parameters.with`\n- `count(\"query\", params)` → `em.createQuery(\"SELECT COUNT(e) FROM ... WHERE ...\", Long.class).getSingleResult()`\n- `count(\"field\", value)` → Similar count query with positional parameter\n- All find operations converted to standard JPQL queries\n\n### 5. **FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Key changes:**\n- Removed `Parameters` import\n- `find(\"primaryKey\", key).firstResultOptional()` → `Optional.ofNullable(em.find(FollowRelationshipEntity.class, key))`\n- `persistAndFlush(entity)` → `em.persist(entity); em.flush()`\n\n### 6. **TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Key changes:**\n- Removed `Parameters` import\n- All Panache find queries converted to standard JPQL with EntityManager\n\n### 7. **TagRepositoryPanache.java**\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/TagRepositoryPanache.java`\n\n**Key changes:**\n- Removed `Parameters` import\n- `listAll()` → `em.createQuery(\"FROM TagEntity\", TagEntity.class).getResultList()`\n- All find operations converted to standard JPQL queries\n\n## Conversion Patterns Applied\n\nAll files now use standard JPA patterns:\n- **Persistence:** `em.persist()` and `em.flush()` instead of Panache methods\n- **Queries:** JPQL with `em.createQuery()` instead of Panache shorthand\n- **Parameters:** Direct `.setParameter()` calls instead of `Parameters.with()`\n- **Counting:** `SELECT COUNT(e)` queries instead of Panache `count()`\n- **Finding by ID:** `em.find()` instead of `findByIdOptional()`\n- **Deletion:** `em.remove()` with `em.merge()` when necessary\n- **Pagination:** `.setFirstResult()` and `.setMaxResults()` instead of `Page.of()`\n- **Sorting:** `ORDER BY` clauses in JPQL instead of `Sort.descending()`\n\nAll files maintain the same class structure with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@AllArgsConstructor` annotations and continue to extend `AbstractPanacheRepository` (which now uses EntityManager internally)."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9cccbbd3-df4b-4bdc-8bbb-45d794239170","uuid":"1b02e4f3-cb0e-4ed7-b9e0-7485dc12b8e6"}
