{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_011GSaWpMkzbBq12YDLYD3Fg","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All the changes have been successfully applied. Let me create a summary of what was done:\n\n## Summary\n\nI have successfully fixed CDI injection for all repository classes and resource/utility classes in the project. The issue was that these classes were using Lombok's `@AllArgsConstructor` for CDI constructor injection, which doesn't work reliably with standard Weld CDI.\n\n### Changes Applied\n\nAll 15 files have been updated with the following pattern:\n\n1. **Removed** `@AllArgsConstructor` annotation\n2. **Removed** `lombok.AllArgsConstructor` import\n3. **Added** `jakarta.inject.Inject` import\n4. **Changed** all fields from `private final` to non-final\n5. **Added** `@Inject` annotation to each field that needs CDI injection\n\n### Files Modified\n\n#### Repository Classes (7 files):\n1. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/UserRepositoryPanache.java`\n2. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/ArticleRepositoryPanache.java`\n3. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/CommentRepositoryPanache.java`\n4. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/panache/FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache.java`\n5. `/home/bmcginn/git/s