ions__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java`\n14. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/SlugifySlugProvider.java`\n15. `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java`\n\n### Key Changes Made\n\n- **ArticlesResource**: Changed `@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- **TagsResource**: Same change for ObjectMapper field\n- **UsersResource**: Changed `@Inject private final JwtTokenProvider tokenProvider;` to `@Inject JwtTokenProvider tokenProvider;`\n- **UserResource**: Field already had `@Inject`, just removed `@AllArgsConstructor` and made field non-final\n\nAll classes now use proper field-level injection with `@Inject` annotations, which is the standard and reliable approach for CDI injection in Jakarta EE and Weld CDI containers."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9cccbbd3-df4b-4bdc-8bbb-45d794239170","uuid":"a2d2fd65-dc4a-4df2-b2ff-5e48a1370f81"}
