{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NndZVkkHdWMSq2H3D9cWYX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The problem is that `weld-se-shaded` and `weld-servlet-shaded` are uber JARs that include Jandex classes within them. The shade plugin can't override classes already embedded in those JARs. I need to either:\n\n1. Exclude Jandex from Weld shaded JARs (not possible since they're embedded)\n2. Use non-shaded Weld instead\n3. Or use the shade plugin's filter to exclude Jandex classes from the weld JARs\n\nLet me use the shade plugin filter to exclude the old Jandex classes from weld JARs:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4263,"cache_read_input_tokens":69277,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4263,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":638},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9cccbbd3-df4b-4bdc-8bbb-45d794239170","uuid":"12529089-c4a7-4348-a34e-5d088e5e1ea4"}
